description: This header file declares initialization and shutdown functions for the device service event handler module in a C project. It contains include guards, includes <stdbool.h>, and defines two functions: deviceServiceEventHandlerInit and deviceServiceEventHandlerShutdown.

methods.name: deviceServiceEventHandlerInit
methods.description: Initializes the device service event handler module.

methods.name: deviceServiceEventHandlerShutdown
methods.description: Shuts down the device service event handler module.
